---
<section id="sponsor">
  <div class="sponsor-box">
    <div class="heart">♥</div>
    <h2>Support mdwow</h2>
    <p>
      If mdwow saves you time, consider sponsoring its development.
      Your support helps keep the project maintained and growing.
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://github.com/sponsors/tianhaoz95"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      class="btn btn-amber"
    >
      Sponsor on GitHub ↗
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .sponsor-box {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-accent);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .heart {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--amber);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  p {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 400px;
  }
</style>
